         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">The requirement contains the following elements: <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Procedures for identification of each confined space and informing employees by
                     sign, placard, training program, or other effective means.</li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">Procedures for the selection and use of personal protective equipment necessary
